summary: A custom face file for Enhanced Character Edit
descriptionHtml:
Pretty simple mod, just the .slot file, screenshots, and a readme with installation instructions.

I apologize for the quality of the screenshots. My computer will only run Skyrim at 800x600 on Low quality. If anyone wants to upload screenshots using a better graphics setup, to really bring out the true beauty, I'd be more than willing to use those as the main images - with full credit to the uploader, of course!

Also, if anyone wants to make a follower, enemy, romance option, etc., based on her, go right ahead. I'll probably even use whatever mod you come up with! Just make sure to credit me for the original face. Or don't, I actually don't really care.
author: AlduinWorldEater
